<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Welcome to RatedDocs</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; background-color: #f9f9fc; margin: 0; padding: 40px 20px; color: #333333; }
    .card { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5, #3b82f6); padding: 30px; text-align: center; color: white; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; }
    .content { padding: 40px 30px; line-height: 1.6; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #4f46e5; color: white !important; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; background-color: #f3f4f6; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to RatedDocs!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
      <p>Thank you for signing up to RatedDocs. We are excited to have you on board.</p>
      <p>To get started, check out your dashboard:</p>
      <p style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; 2026 RatedDocs. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
